{"tid":467704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"工人姐姐就黎返鄉下，好唔捨得","createTime":"2017-11-13T17:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T11:11:38.000Z","uid":90538,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"440968f33ce05fce825c2662a787c3e11c281bc3","tid":467704,"uid":90538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:26:04.000Z","msg":"呢個姐姐係屋企雖然做左短短兩年，但佢對我一家人好好。 屋企相對其他家庭多野做？，姐姐有時可能要做到12點先有得訓，第二日8點又要起過身。其實工人姐姐好辛苦，各位如果屋企有工人姐姐，一定要好好對佢，佢地搵得四千蚊，但又要離郷別井...<br />\n<br />\n講到尾，姐姐下星期走，各位巴絲有無禮物建議送俾姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326b3c8b06a705defc92732251adeddac55f1efd","tid":467704,"uid":61207,"like":5,"dislike":22,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:27:11.000Z","msg":"又無扑過野 會有幾唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1907beac91bf8ccc96a66c1b0ef80755c6c06a3","tid":467704,"uid":88817,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"錢囉"},{"pid":"e36ee025532d5c00ecc108fe6761f71933dcec5a","tid":467704,"uid":129186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:27:49.000Z","msg":"點解返鄉下？"},{"pid":"662029050a0f685b552951447cac753e3943fefa","tid":467704,"uid":8345,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:28:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33ae7e3fa0c909107789e795250fab2258cd375c","tid":467704,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩post嚟"},{"pid":"c02bbdb936f272c61097a95d60519b0b7233de3e","tid":467704,"uid":90538,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:39:53.000Z","msg":"人係感情動物，姐姐係到照顧左我兩年"},{"pid":"a9df236233a2d0e88c9337be8ac07e97cf66150f","tid":467704,"uid":137626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T17:57:48.000Z","msg":"天下無不散之延席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmo